game:decorbazaar-quickstart-text: Thank you for using my mod! This mod adds decorative items to the game. If anyone would love to help develop the mod, please contact me on discord @anyanana. Thank you to @EightTonnesOfCrab on discord for the bath functionality and thank you @Feidry for the stove/firepit functionality! Thank you to RikeiR for translating to Japanese! Enjoy! New blocks with 1.1.6: new metal sconces, new wood sconces, single bald cypress sink is now liberated and has all wood types and stone types to match basic wood kitchen set and stone kitchen set. Single sinks can hold water like double sinks. I have also liberated the cottage core table and stool, improving the models and allowing for all types of wood variants. The cottage core tables now have a double table (with candles) and a single version (with no candles). The cottage core stool now has the original version + a stool with a back. List of Items: Ovens: These function as ovens, naturally. There are 7 types, 3 free-standing, 3 table top, and one meant to be put in the wall. To place the free standing ovens, you MUST place a temporary block where you would like to put the oven first. It can be a dirt block. Then you will place the free-standing oven on top of the temporary block, and then destroy the temporary block. Viola! An oven with fancy stuff underneath. Iron Oven is build to be placed in a wall. Stone Oven is a free-standing oven (see note above!). Oven with Glass is a free-standing oven (see note above!). Fancy Oven with Glass is a free-standing oven (see note above!). Table Stone Oven Table Oven with Glass Fancy Table Oven with Glass Stoves: These stoves now function as firepits! Thanks @Feidry! Stone Stove Cast Iron Stove Cast Iron Stove with Firewood Cast Iron Stove V2 Cast Iron Fireplace Bathroom Decor: Victorian Toilet Victorian Sink Claw Foot Tub allows for 100 buckets of water to fill up. Washing Tub Linen Basket Clothes Line Towel Rack Carpets: Carpets come in blue, dark black, gingham red, green, neutral, red, white, white dotted, yellow flower, dark fancy, and dark floral. Beds: All beds are functional :) Brass Bed Coffin Bed Flower Bed Purple Bed Tables: Side Tables right click to change variant. Brass Table Coffee Table :right click to change variant. Cottage Core Tables have all wood variants and have a single and double version Gothic Table Storage: some have food storage times. Meat Storage. Model and textures by BORGAR on Discord. Thank you! Has spoilage rate. Linen Storage Bone Storage Fat Storage Honey Storage Sewing Shelf Twine Storage Wall Veggie Storage has spoilage rate. Veggie Storage has spoilage rate. Bread Box has spoilage rate. Compost Bin will accelerate rot depending on outside temp. Wardrobe Clutter: Cooking Clutter Forraging Clutter Kitchen Clutter Bathroom Clutter Kitchen: All of the cabinet variants now have inner or corner types for those of you who want L shaped kitchens! Left Cabinet has storage slots. Right Cabinet has storage slots. Left Upper Cabinet has storage slots. Right Upper Cabinet has storage slots. Open Cabinet Sinks: All sinks are able to contain water! To do this, you must place the water block (creative), or empty a bucket onto the block you want to place the sink/water source. The, you place the sink on top of where the water is flowing. If done correctly, it should stop overflowing and be completely contained within the sink. Infinite water! Single Stone Sinks are designed to match the stone kitchen set. Wood Sinks are designed to match the basic wood kitchen set. Wood Sink the left side of the sink is what contains the water. Double Stone Sink the left side of the sink is what contains the water. Stone Cabinet & Island has storage slots. Stone Drawer & Island has storage slots. Stone Upper Cabinet has storage slots. Stone Shelf has storage slots. Fancy Cabinet & Island has storage slots. Fancy Upper Cabinet has storage slots. Kitchen Decor: Ceramic Yellow Pot Jug Glass Tray Table Setting :right click to change variant. Deco Shelf Dish Rack Pots and Pans Mug Rack Bread Basket Tea Sets Spice Rack has storage. Kitchen Shelf Herb Rack Lamps: All Lamps are functional. Candelabras now have aged variant as well as most metal variants. Metal Lamps Right click to change type. Metal Sconces Wood Sconces Goth Lamp Tall Candelabra Table Candelabra Seating: Cottage Core Stool Cottage Core Chair Fabric Chair Wood Stool Sofas Victorian Lounge Chair Gothic Love Seat Fancy Gothic Chair Gothic Foot Rest Garden Decor: Garden Signs Bee Sign Potting Bench has storage slots for seeds. Seed Storage has storage slots for seeds. Terra Cotta Flower Pots are functional! Blue Flower Pot is functional! Purple Flower Pot is functional! Curtains: Curtains work where you right click to change whether you want the top (with the rod), middle, or bottom variant to be expressed for each block. There are currently a plain type and a fancy type. The color variants are: black, blue, brown, gray, green, orange, pink, plain, purple, red, white, and yellow. Mail Boxes: Mail Boxes are just decorative. Random Stuff: Butter Churn Wooden Shelf : right click to change variant. Witchy Items Cartographer Map Brass Mirror Brass Candle Shelf Brass Mushroom Cloche Pile of Letters Graves : right click to change variant. Tile Blocks: Beige Tile Gray Tile Anthro Tile Aged Purple Tile Mossy Pink Tile Gold Square Tile Gold Meteor Tile Paintings available at Luxury, Furniture, and Artisan Traders! Fields of Grain House on the Hill Lone Grave White Flower Wallpapers available at Luxury, Furniture, and Artisan Traders!
